comments.body:
This can be shortened a lot. Remove these explicit functions and roll them into getNumConnections. All the cases can be implemented like this this:

```
LOCK(cs_vNodes);
if(flags == CONNECTIONS_ALL) // Shortcut if we want total
    return vNodes.size();
int nNum = 0;
BOOST_FOREACH(CNode* pnode, vNodes)
if (flags & (pnode->fInbound ? CONNECTIONS_IN : CONNECTIONS_OUT))
    nNum++;
return mNum;
```

Then the flags values should be:

```
enum NumConnections {
    CONNECTIONS_NONE = 0,
    CONNECTIONS_OUT  = (1U << 0),
    CONNECTIONS_IN = (1U << 1),
    CONNECTIONS_ALL  = CONNECTIONS_OUT | CONNECTIONS_IN,
};
```

